    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"breathing and feeling\" is exactly the problem though. feeling is just experiencing more pain, more anxiety, more longing for something that isn't even there. it feels like we're just forced to endure this constant, heavy weight for no reason at all. if there's no grand purpose, then why are we even required to suffer through it? it feels so irrational to keep pushing forward when the math just doesn't add up.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
